examples.en: The referee whistled and the game began.
She whistled a song to me.
Adam whistled happily on his way to work.
Dad whistled to us to come home for dinner.
The spear whistled harmlessly over his head.
He whistled the tune and tapped out the rhythm.
After a long senseless talk she whistled him off at last.
Lucie whistled sharply to catch the other girl's attention.
The girl blushed when a young man whistled as she walked by.
